# CHOPCHOP Integration with CRISPResso2

CRISPResso2 has been extended with CHOPCHOP for guide RNA design.

## Key Components

- [tools/chopchop/chopchop.py](mdc:tools/chopchop/chopchop.py): Core CHOPCHOP script for guide RNA design
- [tools/chopchop/chopchop_integration.py](mdc:tools/chopchop/chopchop_integration.py): Integration script for CRISPResso2
- [tools/chopchop/example_workflow.py](mdc:tools/chopchop/example_workflow.py): Example workflow combining guide design and analysis

## Workflow

The typical workflow involves:

1. Use CHOPCHOP to design optimal guide RNAs
2. Run experiments with the selected guides
3. Analyze editing outcomes with CRISPResso2

## Usage Example

```python
# Design guides
python tools/chopchop/chopchop_integration.py --genome hg38 --target BRCA1 --output chopchop_results

# Analyze editing outcomes
CRISPResso --fastq_r1 sample.fastq --amplicon_seq ACTGACTG...
```

For a complete end-to-end workflow:

```python
python tools/chopchop/example_workflow.py --genome hg38 --target BRCA1 --fastq_r1 sample.fastq --output workflow_results
```

See [tools/chopchop/README_CRISPResso2.md](mdc:tools/chopchop/README_CRISPResso2.md) for more details.
